{"tid":674033,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"P.A.WORKS 「クロムクロ」(黑骸) 續篇製作決定","createTime":"2018-05-22T11:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T12:01:04.000Z","uid":183666,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a8711172474e360a64506d92bc6e05e330ec9bb4","tid":674033,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdnx.natalie.mu/media/news/comic/2018/0522/h1_fixw_640_hq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdnx.natalie.mu%2Fmedia%2Fnews%2Fcomic%2F2018%2F0522%2Fh1_fixw_640_hq.jpg&h=74f3bea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電視動畫「黑骸」後日談小說「クロムクロ 秒速29万kmの亡霊」將於6月1日起以電子書形式出售。<br />\n<br />\n「黑骸 秒速 29 萬公里的亡靈」是動畫製作公司P.A. WORKS推出的電子書專門品牌「P.A.BOOKS」的第二部作品，講述電視動畫最終回白羽由希奈和索菲等人踏上宇宙航艦後的故事，由電視動畫系列構成檜垣亮執筆，導演岡村天斎負責故事監修。 封面和插圖由人物設計石井百合子繪畫。 這部作品會以單集形式出售，每個月的1・15日左右發佈最新話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://natalie.mu/comic/news/283188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnatalie.mu%2Fcomic%2Fnews%2F283188&d=4%2Fonko0djVBA3rAAniKUfgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0460cec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://natalie.mu/comic/news/283188</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pa-works.jp/pabooks/books/kuromukuro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pa-works.jp%2Fpabooks%2Fbooks%2Fkuromukuro&d=4%2Fonko0djVBA3rAAniKUfgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4a24f9f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.pa-works.jp/pabooks/books/kuromukuro</a>"},{"pid":"58c99111ffbf9332f28d9a6a8f653c1296961dc3","tid":674033,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ????"},{"pid":"0640eae0cdf0ea74fb108786341dcf19d7a41aa0","tid":674033,"uid":125203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:14:36.000Z","msg":"小說咋 又無動畫"},{"pid":"4a178d0e8f9320429bead114d6259f